    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318210/extras/af7f01ecdf48efc3cd3fdd559cf136b9.avif?t=1765640861\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318210/extras_big/af7f01ecdf48efc3cd3fdd559cf136b9.avif?t=1765640861 width=800 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318210/extras/1182f22af42cf0d376dbdec8b8a0387f.poster.avif?t=1765640861\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318210/extras/1182f22af42cf0d376dbdec8b8a0387f.webm?t=1765640861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318210/extras/1182f22af42cf0d376dbdec8b8a0387f.mp4?t=1765640861\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「网络世界中也有真正的朋友！」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角陈多妍是一款有偶像角色登场的日本游戏《偶像☆星》的狂热御宅族。某天，主角和朋友像往常一样在玩游戏时，得知这款游戏的角色香水周边将在日本限量发售，于是主角就顺势接下了香水团购的责任。然而，主角却一时冲动，把团购集来的钱全都用作了个人用途。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318210/extras/0a4a18ac7fa66defaf7f518b5805b3f5.poster.avif?t=1765640861\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318210/extras/0a4a18ac7fa66defaf7f518b5805b3f5.webm?t=1765640861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318210/extras/0a4a18ac7fa66defaf7f518b5805b3f5.mp4?t=1765640861\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「偶像☆星」香水团购的订购截止日只剩下14天……主角能在14天内再次筹到500万韩元，顺利订购香水吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318210/extras/deac253b312959f5843e50884d48bdaa.poster.avif?t=1765640861\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318210/extras/deac253b312959f5843e50884d48bdaa.webm?t=1765640861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318210/extras/deac253b312959f5843e50884d48bdaa.mp4?t=1765640861\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是引导主角走向毁灭，还是帮助她改过自新，成为一名合格的社会人，都取决于玩家的选择，体验多样且激动人心的结局吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~特色~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318210/extras/42a73e3dbfc22fc4580e148538ad3168.poster.avif?t=1765640861\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318210/extras/42a73e3dbfc22fc4580e148538ad3168.webm?t=1765640861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318210/extras/42a73e3dbfc22fc4580e148538ad3168.mp4?t=1765640861\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受现实和网络世界中的各种迷你游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318210/extras/96e6d4c1e4bac755aa7678c09cb04912.poster.avif?t=1765640861\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318210/extras/96e6d4c1e4bac755aa7678c09cb04912.webm?t=1765640861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318210/extras/96e6d4c1e4bac755aa7678c09cb04912.mp4?t=1765640861\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的选择将影响角色的好感度，试着攻略各种角色吧。</p>",
